p #{toName},
p
  | A new user has registered on 
  a(href="#{siteLink}" target="_blank") #{siteLink}
  | . Here are the details of their account:
div
  table(cellpadding="0" cellspacing="2" border="0")
    tr
      td(valign="top" style="padding-right: 1em;") Username:
      td #{userUsername}
    tr
      td(valign="top" style="padding-right: 1em;") Name:
      td #{userName}
